column5: Just putting a dent in the Trent River Pike population while waiting for walleye to open.  These things are tasty at this time of the year.  Our group caught over 40 pike in a few days.  Kept some for eating, but let the smaller ones go back.
nice! Where about on the Trent? The pike bite has been crazy where we are too,,
Nice gators, man i cant wait for opener here and my trip lol.
